@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
actor 运营 
participant "商家管理后台" as A
participant "presell-pay" as B
participant "银准" as C
participant "DB层" as D
运营 -> A: 1.根据付款账号查询商户余额
activate A
A -> B: 2.根据付款账号查询余额信息
activate B
B -> C: 3.根据付款账号和\n biz_type = mchaccnt.balance.query 查询余额
activate C
C --> B: 4.返回商户余额
deactivate C
B --> A: 6.返回余额
deactivate B
A --> 运营: 显示余额信息
deactivate A
@enduml